{"ts":"2026-06-26T13:32:43.674Z","author":"claude-code-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-q0ye"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"CodeFactor/Maintainability: clear remaining unicorn lints (no-thenable ×4, no-useless-spread ×2, no-useless-length-check ×1)"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Three small `eslint-plugin-unicorn` rule groups (7 findings total, Maintainability).\n\n### 1. `no-thenable` ×4 — https://www.codefactor.io/repository/github/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/main?category=Maintainability&groupId=10592\n\nA member named `then` makes an object look like a Promise (a \"thenable\") and can break `await`/Promise resolution. **Confirmed:** `src/sdk/cli-contracts.ts:2483` and `src/sdk/cli-contracts.ts:2493` (`then:` keys) — this is the main reason `cli-contracts.ts` is the #1 B-rated hotspot.\n\n⚠️ **Risk:** `then` here is part of the CLI-contracts data surface. Before renaming, check whether the key is a public contract consumed by the SDK / snapshot and whether `pnpm contracts:check` or any consumer depends on it. May require a coordinated rename + snapshot regen, or a scoped CodeFactor ignore if the key is contractual.\n\n### 2. `no-useless-spread` ×2 — https://www.codefactor.io/repository/github/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/main?category=Maintainability&groupId=10584\n\nRedundant spread, e.g. `[...[a, b]]`, `{ ...{ a } }`, or `new Set([...iterable])` where the spread is unnecessary. Drop the spread.\n\n### 3. `no-useless-length-check` ×1 — https://www.codefactor.io/repository/github/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/main?category=Maintainability&groupId=10597\n\nRedundant `arr.length === 0 || arr.every(...)` (every() on empty is already true) or `arr.length > 0 && arr.some(...)` (some() on empty is already false). Drop the length check.\n\n## Fix\n\n#2 and #3 are mechanical/auto-fixable. #1 needs the contract-safety check above. Keep tests + 100% coverage + typecheck green."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Chore"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["code-quality","codefactor","eslint","maintainability"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-06-26T13:32:43.674Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-26T13:32:43.674Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"claude-code-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"CodeFactor reports 0 findings for no-thenable, no-useless-spread, and no-useless-length-check; the cli-contracts.ts `then` rename (if applied) does NOT break the contracts snapshot (pnpm contracts:check) or any SDK consumer; full coverage suite + typecheck green."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-92if"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"7edf7d36f6eb5a93322cc272be541dbf723818e2a9762a4c02f420e0504fc3b0","message":""}
